Sentencas: DC and ac impedance measurements were performed on yittria-stabilized ZrO2 electrolytes to separate bulk properties from interfacial phenomena.
Titulo: Characterization of solid oxide fuel cells by use of an internal Pt voltage probe

Sentencas: A Pt voltage probe was buried directly into the solid yittria-stabilizied ZrO2 electrolyte via screen-printing tape cast layers.
Titulo: Characterization of solid oxide fuel cells by use of an internal Pt voltage probe

Sentencas: DC measurements of solid oxide fuel cells were performed with an internal Pt voltage probe to determine ohmic and nonohmic drops for the total cell during operation.
Titulo: Characterization of solid oxide fuel cells by use of an internal Pt voltage probe

Sentencas: AC impedance measurements were also utilized to show a good correlation between the total cell impedance and the sum of the two half-cell impedances.
Titulo: Characterization of solid oxide fuel cells by use of an internal Pt voltage probe
